					<div class="rounded-2xl p-5 my-4 border border-gray-200" style="background-color: white;">
						<h4 class="font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;">Drill 1: The Price is Right</h4>
						<p>Look at price tags around your house. Say the number in Tibetan. "This costs <span class="tibetan-text">ལྔ་བརྒྱ</span>." Do it until you don't have to think.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="rounded-2xl p-5 my-4 border border-gray-200" style="background-color: white;">
						<h4 class="font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;">Drill 2: Count Your Steps</h4>
						<p>For one day, count your steps in Tibetan. Just to twenty, then start over. It forces speed and automaticity.</p>
